//@version=5

// ============================================================================
// Catch Raise v4.4.22.2 – BTC (Audit + ADDON Tuning)
// ============================================================================
//
// CHANGELOG (from v4.4.22.1):
//
// 1) ADDON ENGINE DIAGNOSTICS & TUNING
//    - Investigated ADDON funnel bottlenecks using diagnostic counters.
//    - Identified restrictive touch detection and cooldown gating.
//    - Adjusted ADDON parameters for testing:
//
//        Touch detection buffer:
//            emaFast + ATR * 0.20
//
//        addOnRequireProfitPct:
//            reduced (diagnostic test)
//
//        addOnRequireMfePct:
//            reduced to allow earlier trend pressing
//
//        addOnCooldownBars:
//            reduced to improve ADDON participation
//
//    - Result:
//        ADDON engine activates more frequently while maintaining
//        trend structure validation.
//
// 2) ADDON TOUCH MODEL UPDATE
//    - Broadened pullback detection around Fast EMA to allow shallow
//      continuation pauses common in strong BTC trends.
//    - Previous strict requirement often missed valid continuation setups.
//
// 3) MARKER AUDIT (visual validation)
//    - Begin verification that chart markers reflect actual fill paths:
//          PB_BASE
//          CONT
//          ADDON
//          EXIT
//
//    - Ensure markers correspond to position-increase events
//      rather than signal conditions.
//
// 4) PLOT CLEANUP (visual debugging)
//    - Separate colors for major indicators to improve chart readability:
//          Fast EMA
//          Mid EMA
//          Slow EMA
//          Donchian bands
//          RSI
//
//    - Previous versions used similar colors making diagnostics difficult.
//
// GOAL:
// - Stabilize ADDON behavior after tuning.
// - Verify marker correctness for accurate chart interpretation.
// - Improve chart readability for strategy debugging.
// - Prepare for focused CONT entry evaluation.
//
// NEXT STEPS (future versions):
// - Review CONT_SIGNAL logic to confirm strong-trend entries are not missed.
// - Verify PB_BASE and CONT independence in ENTRY_ORCH.
// - Evaluate ADDON frequency vs profitability after tuning.
// - Potential refinement of early-trend entry conditions.
// ============================================================================

